When deleting a project using the UiTestSuites you will get the following 
exception from QuickDiff. This causes two failures using the contents of HEAD 
for platform-ui and platform-core with the rest of Eclipse loaded as binaries 
running the IWorkbenchPageTest.

This is currently breaking the UIsuites.

STEPS
1) Load org.eclipse.ui.tests
2) Load platform-ui and platform-core modules
3) Load all other plug-ins as binaries
4) Replace the tearDown method in IDeprecatedWorkbenchPageTest with the 
following (all this does is print the stack trace)

